column5: Leaving Friday for Pakwash and would like a recent report. What's the water level like? Mayflies finished? FISHING?????????? Thanks Brad

Bring your rubber boots, Water is 4 feet higher than normal. The levels are as high as it was in 1992. One good thing fishing has been good but it takes a bit to find them. The fishing is different compaired to previous years. Have a Good trip.
